{"tid":1547514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【烏克蘭】基輔郵報表態：我哋必定與每一個香港人一齊捍衛民主！","createTime":"2019-09-06T16:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T17:28:54.000Z","uid":47630,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"54de1751f7016e4416b57a2f1507999707f58dd6","tid":1547514,"uid":47630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uohi42T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuohi42T.png&h=da18ebe4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢張圖係嚟自烏克蘭人開嘅page: <a href=\"https://facebook.com/ufhkc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fufhkc%2F&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2gESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=646b3898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/ufhkc/</a><br />\n<br />\n內文好長，有興趣嘅巴絲打可以開嚟睇下，source我擺咗係下面！<br />\n我知大家懶，為咗方便大家閱讀，我幫手總結下<br />\n內文大概就係：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">頂住啊，香港人！我哋烏克蘭一定會企係你哋香港人嗰邊，為民主而戰！</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以，支持下佢哋得唔得香港人！<br />\n唔好俾佢哋心淡啊！like下佢哋嘅Facebook好唔好！<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/ufhkc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fufhkc%2F&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2gESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=646b3898\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/ufhkc/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kyivpost.com/article/opinion/editorial/hong-kong-win.html?fbclid=IwAR3kSh-mizxklCH5YZuM8wczXIog8-UbfSO23fyamaWxVNiNg79cBQC0_JA&amp;cn-reloaded=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kyivpost.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Feditorial%2Fhong-kong-win.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3kSh-mizxklCH5YZuM8wczXIog8-UbfSO23fyamaWxVNiNg79cBQC0_JA%26cn-reloaded%3D1&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2gESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=5222a38f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kyivpost.com/article/opinion/editorial/hong-kong-win.html?fbclid=IwAR3kSh-mizxklCH5YZuM8wczXIog8-UbfSO23fyamaWxVNiN